11:54.803 --> 11:59.001
...I do a live web chat
called Apartment Talk on Tuesday nights.

12:01.544 --> 12:03.512
No backsies.

12:08.817 --> 12:11.684
Sheldon, dinner.

12:18.394 --> 12:19.452
What is this?

12:20.329 --> 12:24.390
This is the difference
between eating and dining.

12:27.469 --> 12:29.437
Remarkable.

12:29.605 --> 12:34.804
I'm just realizing how much Leonard's
been skating by all these years.

12:36.011 --> 12:37.205
It's not a big thing.

12:37.379 --> 12:40.507
Just think of me
as a brown Martha Stewart.

12:40.916 --> 12:42.440
[KNOCKING ON DOOR]

12:42.651 --> 12:45.449
Hey, Sheldon, did you change
your Wi-Fi password again?

12:45.621 --> 12:49.079
