That's big.

13:30.366 --> 13:34.325
No. Origami napkin swans.

13:36.138 --> 13:38.368
That's the headline.

13:39.275 --> 13:41.334
It's a good thing.

13:43.078 --> 13:45.603
So do you know
what kind of research you'll be doing...

13:45.781 --> 13:47.373
...at this pharmaceutical company?

13:47.549 --> 13:49.983
