for the premature ejaculation project.

13:58.560 --> 14:02.223
I mean, it's not like either one of us
has heart disease.

14:06.068 --> 14:08.263
Oh, I almost forgot,
I got you a little present.

14:08.437 --> 14:10.803
Oh, Bernie, no, you didn't have to.

14:10.973 --> 14:14.101
Well, I wanted to. Come on, open it.

14:16.979 --> 14:19.880
You bought me a Rolex?

14:20.049 --> 14:22.074
How much did this cost?

14:22.251 --> 14:24.219
Oh, you let me worry about the money.

14:27.256 --> 14:29.383
I just want my baby
to have pretty things.

14:34.997 --> 14:38.194
- More wine?
