15:19.108 --> 15:20.302
Good night.

15:20.476 --> 15:22.706
Please note, it is now past 10 p.m.

15:22.878 --> 15:26.279
Per our roommate agreement,
kindly refrain from raucous laughter...

15:26.448 --> 15:29.349
