for you to think:

15:42.131 --> 15:45.589
"Oh, Krishna,
I've got to get me some of that"?

15:46.602 --> 15:49.400
It's better than having to wear
noise-canceling headphones...

15:49.571 --> 15:50.629
...in my own apartment.

15:50.806 --> 15:52.671
What? Oh, God, yeah, yeah.

15:52.841 --> 15:55.469
- Leonard's a noisy little dude in the sack.
- Mm.

15:55.644 --> 15:57.407
