16:06.188 --> 16:08.247
Yeah, sorry, sorry.

16:10.192 --> 16:12.558
- Can I tell you a secret?
- Yeah.

16:13.295 --> 16:14.762
I screwed up.

16:14.930 --> 16:18.696
Leonard's a great guy.
I never should have broken up with him.

16:19.902 --> 16:22.166
