16:39.888 --> 16:42.789
...and you hadn't brought up
that creepy pornography story...

16:42.958 --> 16:47.054
...l'd be on you like the speed of light
squared on matter to make energy.

16:47.229 --> 16:50.494
Hey, you totally got that right.
