17:10.018 --> 17:11.781
LEONARD:
Mm.

17:15.858 --> 17:19.259
Leonard, sweetheart,
we're kissing, not eating hot soup.

17:20.796 --> 17:22.286
Sorry.

17:23.532 --> 17:25.329
[COMPUTER BEEPING]

17:26.368 --> 17:29.235
That's my parents on video chat.
Go hide in the bedroom.

17:29.404 --> 17:32.066
Oh, come on,
why don't we just tell them we're dating?

17:32.241 --> 17:34.141
We've been through this, it's not time.

17:34.309 --> 17:36.834
- When is the time?
- I've got five brothers and sisters.

17:37.012 --> 17:40.243
One of them is bound to screw up,
then I'll tell my parents about you.

17:40.415 --> 17:42.349
- Now shoo.
- Fine.

17:44.786 --> 17:46.481
Hello, Mommy. Hello, Daddy.

17:46.655 --> 17:48.646
